/*@!Encoding:1252*/
//*		REMARKS:           																		*
//*         Add also Tr_Description.can before you add TRLib.can in inculde files section		*
//*		    in CAPL.                                                                            *
//*			                                                                                    *
//*		APPLICATION NOTES:  																	*
//*         How to build test report in test case (following order should be kept):				*
//*			    1. Init_Test_Case_Report(Identifier, Title, Description, TestCaseID, Req, Params)*
//*			    2. STEP() - automaticly increment step number in test report or                 *
//*                STEP(FALSE) - as STEP() but number will be showed only                       *
//*                              when in next step ACTION will be used                          *
//*             3. STEP_Nb(value) - optional, it sets step number to [value]                    *
//*				3. use ACTION, ACTION_DATA, EXPECTED, EXPECTED_DATA, OBSERVED, OBSERVED_DATA,   *   
//*                COMMENT, COMMENT_DATA functions from TR_Description.can                      *
//*             4. Add_To_Report() - all added data in step 3 will apear in report w/o verdict, *
//*                             or                                                              * 
//*                Add_To_Report(PASSED[|NO_TS_NUMBER]) - as AddToReport()                      *
//*                                                     but with verdict PASSED, or             *
//*                Add_To_Report(FAILED[|NO_TS_NUMBER]) - as AddToReport()                      *
//*                                                     but with verdict FAILED, or             *
//*                Add_To_Report(N_A[|NO_TS_NUMBER]) - as AddToReport()                         *
//*                                                     but tehre is no verdict                 *
//*                Add_To_Report(WARNING[|NO_TS_NUMBER]) - as AddToReport()                     *
//*                                                     but with verdict WARNING,               *
//*                 then clears all added data in step 3                                        *
//*                NO_TS_NUMBER determines if there should be number of testcase in report      *
//*																								*
//***********************************************************************************************
//*																								*
//*		File Revision History																	*
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*		Rev	|	Date	  	| Name	|		Description											*
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*		001	| 	20 11 2008	|  KHO  |	First release.                                          *
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*		002	| 	24 02 2009	|  KHO  |	Added comment_data.                                     *
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*		003	| 	03 03 2009	|  KHO  |	Changes in test report (CR 8):                          *
//*         |               |       |   TCID:: -> TCID: / REQ:: -> REQ: / PARAMS:: -> PARAMS:   *
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*		004	| 	19 03 2009	|  MKU  |	CR  ID 19:                                              *
//*         |               |       |     STEP(byte) updated added 2 new flags:                 *
//*         |               |       |       SHOW_TS_NUMBER, DO_NOT_INC_TS_NUMBER                *
//*         |               |       |     Add_To_Report(byte) - updated                         *
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*		005	| 	02 07 2009	|  KHO  |	CR  ID 45:                                              *
//*         |               |       |     Added new overloaded function:                        *
//*         |               |       |       long Init_Test_Case_Report (char sDescription[],    *
//*         |               |       |                   char sReq[], char sParams[])            *
//*         |               |       |     Removed sTCidentifier and sTCTitle                    *
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*		006	| 	31 08 2010	|  KHO  |	New feature                                             *
//*         |               |       |     Added new function:                                   *
//*         |               |       |       long TC_REQ (char sReq_to_add[])                    *
//*         |               |       |           function add requirements in capl test case     *
//*         |               |       |     it must be used before Init_Test_Case_Report          *
//*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
//***********************************************************************************************
